773
00:53:57,630 --> 00:53:59,090
- [rhythmic knocking]
- [gasps]

774
00:54:01,301 --> 00:54:04,304
[suspenseful music playing]

775
00:54:22,739 --> 00:54:23,573
Henry?

776
00:54:36,586 --> 00:54:37,504
[Esquibel yells]

777
00:54:37,587 --> 00:54:40,924
[in demonic voice]
No one's getting out of here alive!

778
00:54:42,759 --> 00:54:44,511
[laughs] No one.

779
00:54:46,638 --> 00:54:48,640
[thunder rumbling and rain pattering]

780
00:54:54,437 --> 00:54:55,605
[screams]

781
00:55:00,151 --> 00:55:01,694
[rhythmic knocking]

782
00:55:12,288 --> 00:55:13,915
[screams]

783
00:55:14,791 --> 00:55:16,584
- [knocking]
- [whimpering]

784
00:55:17,460 --> 00:55:19,462
- [knocking continues]
- [screams]

785
00:55:19,546 --> 00:55:21,297
- [demonic growling]
- [thuds]

786
00:55:21,381 --> 00:55:24,384
[haunting music playing]

787
00:55:24,467 --> 00:55:25,385
[screams]

788
00:55:27,387 --> 00:55:29,222
[knocking continues]

789
00:55:29,305 --> 00:55:30,223
[screams]

790
00:55:30,306 --> 00:55:31,599
[muffled screaming]

791
00:55:41,109 --> 00:55:43,570
Let's see what secrets you are hiding.

792
00:55:59,210 --> 00:56:02,213
[haunting music playing]

793
00:56:08,052 --> 00:56:09,721
- What happened?
- [Julia screaming]

794
00:56:16,811 --> 00:56:17,645
[Amy screams]

795
00:56:17,729 --> 00:56:18,563
Go!

796
00:56:19,897 --> 00:56:23,026
- [intense music playing]
- [muffled screams]

797
00:56:26,904 --> 00:56:28,323
[gasping]

798
00:56:28,406 --> 00:56:30,366
[Amy screaming]

799
00:56:30,450 --> 00:56:31,743
[demon growls]

800
00:56:32,660 --> 00:56:34,495
[Amy screams] Help me!

801
00:56:34,579 --> 00:56:35,496
Amorth!

802
00:56:37,457 --> 00:56:38,625
[Amy] Help me!

803
00:56:39,584 --> 00:56:41,044
Help!

804
00:56:41,127 --> 00:56:41,961
[Julia] Amy!

805
00:56:43,338 --> 00:56:46,049
[in Latin]
In the name of Christ, let her go.

806
00:56:46,132 --> 00:56:48,426
In the name of Christ, let her go.

807
00:56:48,509 --> 00:56:50,011
- [Amy screams]
- [Julia] Amy!

808
00:56:50,845 --> 00:56:51,679
[Amy] Help!

809
00:56:52,347 --> 00:56:55,141
[Amorth]
In the name of Christ, let her go.

810
00:56:55,224 --> 00:56:56,559
It's me. It's me.

811
00:56:56,643 --> 00:56:58,311
Oh, my God. Oh, Amy.

812
00:56:58,394 --> 00:57:02,065
[Amorth] In the name of Christ,
go away, Satan, go away!

813
00:57:02,148 --> 00:57:03,149
[demon growls]

814
00:57:04,776 --> 00:57:07,779
[ominous music playing]

815
00:57:22,960 --> 00:57:24,379
It's one of her nails.

816
00:57:25,463 --> 00:57:27,757
[Amorth in English]
Tomás, take them to the chapel.

817
00:57:30,259 --> 00:57:33,262
[ominous music continues]

818
00:57:41,979 --> 00:57:44,232
Everything is redacted.

819
00:57:47,902 --> 00:57:50,738
"Our sins will seek us out."

820
00:58:06,838 --> 00:58:08,464
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

821
00:58:08,965 --> 00:58:12,677
You don't get to stay handsome
in this business for too long.

822
00:58:12,760 --> 00:58:14,262
Please. Hm? Don't.

823
00:58:14,345 --> 00:58:19,267
I once have a demon
try to put a crucifix into my eyeball.

824
00:58:19,350 --> 00:58:21,144
You're always talking and talking. Enough.

825
00:58:21,227 --> 00:58:22,770
- Please.
- [shushing]

826
00:58:22,854 --> 00:58:24,272
They're sleeping.

827
00:58:24,355 --> 00:58:25,481
No more stories.

828
00:58:28,943 --> 00:58:32,405
Did you consider why the demon does this?

829
00:58:32,488 --> 00:58:33,781
To scare us, hm?

830
00:58:33,865 --> 00:58:35,158
For what benefit?

831
00:58:35,742 --> 00:58:36,576
Chaos.

832
00:58:38,369 --> 00:58:39,537
Distraction.

833
00:58:39,620 --> 00:58:41,664
The devil is the great deceiver.

834
00:58:41,748 --> 00:58:43,875
He can make you see things from your past.

835
00:58:43,958 --> 00:58:47,754
Apparitions, memories,
always trying to deceive us.

836
00:58:47,837 --> 00:58:51,549
So we never know what he's thinking,
what he's planning.

837
00:58:52,842 --> 00:58:54,510
If you do not believe me...

838
00:58:55,428 --> 00:58:56,679
just ask my friend.

839
00:58:59,766 --> 00:59:02,059
Come, I'll show you what I found.

840
00:59:02,894 --> 00:59:03,853
Amorth!

841
00:59:03,936 --> 00:59:06,022
[Amorth]
I noticed this when I first arrived.

842
00:59:12,236 --> 00:59:13,112
What is this?

843
00:59:14,030 --> 00:59:15,364
You recognize this?

844
00:59:16,282 --> 00:59:18,576
Yes, it's the seal
of the Spanish Inquisition.

845
00:59:18,659 --> 00:59:22,246
<i>Sì.</i> The darkest time
in the history of the Church.

846
00:59:23,206 --> 00:59:24,624
And they are...?

847
00:59:25,500 --> 00:59:28,461
The victims.
The ones who would not convert.

848
00:59:30,838 --> 00:59:32,799
There is something underneath this place.

849
00:59:33,382 --> 00:59:35,510
Something is hidden here. Come.

850
00:59:36,928 --> 00:59:39,931
[ominous music playing]

851
01:00:00,159 --> 01:00:01,035
Hold this.

852
01:00:10,294 --> 01:00:11,879
Two crossed keys.

853
01:00:12,463 --> 01:00:13,548
Do you recognize this?

854
01:00:14,173 --> 01:00:16,384
- It's the Vatican seal.
- [speaks in Italian]

855
01:00:18,094 --> 01:00:20,721
- Is it gas?
- [in English] A little gas.

856
01:00:20,805 --> 01:00:23,683
A little sulfur. A little death.

857
01:00:23,766 --> 01:00:27,061
So no smoking, huh? [chuckles] Stand back.

858
01:00:32,525 --> 01:00:35,528
- [haunting music playing]
- [growls]

859
01:00:39,282 --> 01:00:40,950
It's a door. Push with me.

860
01:00:41,033 --> 01:00:41,868
Okay.

861
01:01:05,099 --> 01:01:06,058
Catacomb.

862
01:01:06,726 --> 01:01:08,936
This is how they would bury the dead.

863
01:01:21,657 --> 01:01:24,452
I understand the Vatican
sealing this place off.

864
01:01:26,579 --> 01:01:28,789
But why would they leave someone?

865
01:01:29,290 --> 01:01:32,043
[Amorth]
The ring of the cardinal protector.

866
01:01:36,881 --> 01:01:40,426
He was the final hope, the last protector.

867
01:01:42,678 --> 01:01:46,557
It looks like he's a prisoner,
but he's not.

868
01:01:47,141 --> 01:01:50,353
The cage is for his own safety.

869
01:01:51,020 --> 01:01:57,860
They do this when an exorcism fails.
To protect against a demon's escape,

870
01:01:57,944 --> 01:02:01,322
to trap something
they need to remain hidden.

871
01:02:04,784 --> 01:02:07,828
Tomás, see if you can open this gate.

872
01:02:17,213 --> 01:02:22,510
[in Latin] "Your cardinal protector writes
to inform you of our worst fears.

873
01:02:22,593 --> 01:02:27,014
A great evil has taken hold
of San Sebastian Abbey.

874
01:02:27,098 --> 01:02:29,892
It must be buried here forever."

875
01:02:32,853 --> 01:02:33,729
It's locked.

876
01:02:34,397 --> 01:02:35,856
Then our friend here...

877
01:02:36,983 --> 01:02:38,401
must have a key.

878
01:02:44,782 --> 01:02:46,742
Where did you hide your key?

879
01:02:51,080 --> 01:02:52,415
In the stomach.

880
01:02:56,544 --> 01:02:57,878
Forgive me.

881
01:02:59,213 --> 01:03:01,632
- [gas hisses]
- [gags, then coughs]

882
01:03:15,020 --> 01:03:16,188
Try this.

883
01:03:19,066 --> 01:03:19,900
Go.

884
01:03:24,363 --> 01:03:27,241
"All attempts at exorcism have failed.

885
01:03:27,324 --> 01:03:30,745
Satan owns this ground now.

886
01:03:31,370 --> 01:03:38,210
I have never seen
a demon this powerful before."

887
01:03:38,294 --> 01:03:40,504
[groaning]

888
01:03:40,588 --> 01:03:42,590
[speaking in Italian]

889
01:03:49,889 --> 01:03:51,015
Gabriele.

890
01:03:51,098 --> 01:03:52,016
Gabriele.

891
01:03:52,099 --> 01:03:54,101
[sirens wailing]

892
01:03:57,104 --> 01:04:00,399
[ominous music playing]

893
01:04:00,483 --> 01:04:01,484
It worked.

894
01:04:01,567 --> 01:04:02,526
Ah.

895
01:04:04,904 --> 01:04:06,238
Thank you, my friend.

896
01:04:10,993 --> 01:04:13,996
[haunting music playing]

897
01:04:14,080 --> 01:04:17,083
- [thumping]
- [girl screaming, then laughing]

898
01:04:19,752 --> 01:04:20,586
Amy?

899
01:04:30,471 --> 01:04:31,680
[Esquibel coughs]

900
01:04:37,603 --> 01:04:40,022
The gases and the sulfur,
it's getting stronger.

901
01:04:42,775 --> 01:04:44,652
We are getting closer to hell.

902
01:05:01,168 --> 01:05:03,337
Cardinal Sullivan, is he all right?

903
01:05:03,420 --> 01:05:04,588
He collapsed.

904
01:05:04,672 --> 01:05:05,840
[Lumumba] Holy Father.

905
01:05:06,841 --> 01:05:08,884
[EKG beeping]

906
01:05:08,968 --> 01:05:11,053
[in Italian] You are just agitated.

907
01:05:11,971 --> 01:05:12,847
[in English] Tell him.

908
01:05:12,930 --> 01:05:14,557
[in English] Tell who?

909
01:05:17,059 --> 01:05:18,310
Gabriele.

910
01:05:18,894 --> 01:05:19,812
Gabriele?

911
01:05:20,896 --> 01:05:22,565
- [speaks in Italian]
- Amorth?

912
01:05:22,648 --> 01:05:25,192
- [EKG beeping rapidly]
- [speaks in Italian]

913
01:05:25,276 --> 01:05:26,443
Amorth?

914
01:05:26,527 --> 01:05:29,113
What trouble has he got us into this time?

915
01:05:32,700 --> 01:05:34,743
[Amorth] The Friar De Ojada.

916
01:05:36,954 --> 01:05:39,582
One of the greatest exorcists of all time.

917
01:05:46,255 --> 01:05:48,090
[Esquibel]
The seal of the Spanish Inquisition.

918
01:05:55,723 --> 01:05:57,224
His journal.

919
01:05:57,308 --> 01:05:58,642
"Today...

920
01:05:59,518 --> 01:06:02,062
I was summoned to the town of Segovia."

921
01:06:02,146 --> 01:06:03,689
A possessed monk.

922
01:06:03,772 --> 01:06:06,609
"In the year of our Lord 1475.

923
01:06:08,235 --> 01:06:11,030
While questioning the demon
possessing the monk,

924
01:06:11,113 --> 01:06:13,741
he answered me from the mouth of another.

925
01:06:14,700 --> 01:06:16,202
And then a third."

926
01:06:17,077 --> 01:06:18,746
Multiple possessions.

927
01:06:18,829 --> 01:06:20,331
It's a powerful demon.

928
01:06:20,414 --> 01:06:21,415
[speaks in Italian]

929
01:06:39,516 --> 01:06:40,392
[Julia] Amy?

930
01:06:40,476 --> 01:06:43,479
[haunting music playing]

931
01:06:45,022 --> 01:06:47,441
[demonic growling]

932
01:06:48,567 --> 01:06:49,944
[Amy laughs]

933
01:06:55,449 --> 01:06:57,952
"The exorcist becomes possessed himself."

934
01:06:58,827 --> 01:06:59,954
Friar De Ojada?

935
01:07:00,037 --> 01:07:03,749
You know he is the man
who convinced Queen Isabella

936
01:07:03,832 --> 01:07:05,709
of the need for an Inquisition?

937
01:07:06,335 --> 01:07:10,381
So that means
from the time he is possessed in 1475,

938
01:07:10,464 --> 01:07:13,634
everything that happens after this...

939
01:07:14,635 --> 01:07:16,053
is the work of the devil.

940
01:07:17,638 --> 01:07:23,018
Centuries of persecution and torture,
the worst abuses of the Inquisition,

941
01:07:23,102 --> 01:07:26,522
all started by the friar
and done in the name of God

942
01:07:27,439 --> 01:07:28,774
by the devil.

943
01:07:30,359 --> 01:07:31,944
The Vatican must have known this.

944
01:07:32,653 --> 01:07:34,321
The Church covered it up.

945
01:07:34,405 --> 01:07:36,407
And they buried the truth here.

946
01:07:36,490 --> 01:07:39,410
"Your sins will seek you out."

947
01:07:39,493 --> 01:07:42,371
The construction work
must have freed the demon.

948
01:07:44,164 --> 01:07:45,165
[Julia] Amy?

949
01:07:45,249 --> 01:07:47,584
[Amy laughing]

950
01:07:51,297 --> 01:07:52,256
Amy?

951
01:07:56,760 --> 01:07:57,594
Henry.

952
01:07:58,637 --> 01:08:00,180
- It's okay, Mommy.
- It's okay, Mommy.

953
01:08:00,764 --> 01:08:02,349
- Henry's okay.
- Henry's okay.

954
01:08:02,433 --> 01:08:03,892
Oh, that's great.

955
01:08:05,269 --> 01:08:07,229
Listen, Amy,
why don't you come downstairs with me?

956
01:08:07,313 --> 01:08:08,939
- I'm sorry, Mom.
- I'm sorry, Mom.

957
01:08:09,023 --> 01:08:11,692
- I don't know what got into me.
- I don't know what got into me.

958
01:08:12,818 --> 01:08:14,236
Well, that's okay.

959
01:08:15,321 --> 01:08:18,365
That's okay.
I just need your sister for a minute. Amy?

960
01:08:18,449 --> 01:08:20,409
- Can you forgive me, Mom?
- Can you forgive me, Mom?

961
01:08:22,244 --> 01:08:24,580
[ominous music playing]

962
01:08:31,754 --> 01:08:34,840
"The great dragon was hurled down.

963
01:08:34,923 --> 01:08:38,635
Hurled into the earth,
where he was bound."

964
01:08:38,719 --> 01:08:41,889
"And his angels with him." Revelations.

965
01:08:42,806 --> 01:08:46,435
Two hundred rogue angels
buried into the earth.

966
01:08:46,518 --> 01:08:49,980
This abbey
is one of those godforsaken places.

967
01:08:50,064 --> 01:08:52,483
This demon, he was trying to find them.

968
01:08:52,566 --> 01:08:56,278
To raise an army and destroy the Church.

969
01:08:56,362 --> 01:08:57,654
Amy, come here.

970
01:08:57,738 --> 01:08:59,907
- What's in your hand, Mommy?
- What's in your hand, Mommy?

971
01:09:00,824 --> 01:09:02,034
Amy, come here, right now.

972
01:09:02,117 --> 01:09:04,995
- What's in your hand, Mommy?
- What's in your hand, Mommy?

973
01:09:08,749 --> 01:09:10,167
- [growls]
- [screams]

974
01:09:10,250 --> 01:09:12,628
[intense music playing]

975
01:09:13,545 --> 01:09:14,922
[growls]

976
01:09:23,847 --> 01:09:24,973
Look.

977
01:09:28,310 --> 01:09:29,561
[demon] Watch me, Mommy.

978
01:09:29,645 --> 01:09:30,771
Watch me.

979
01:09:45,327 --> 01:09:46,328
[Amorth] His name...

980
01:09:48,414 --> 01:09:49,790
the king of hell...

981
01:09:50,958 --> 01:09:52,167
Asmodeus.

982
01:09:52,918 --> 01:09:54,378
[roars]

983
01:10:00,134 --> 01:10:02,177
[EKG beeping rapidly]

984
01:10:02,261 --> 01:10:03,262
Quickly!

985
01:10:07,933 --> 01:10:09,518
[Julia] Amy, use the sedative.

986
01:10:15,482 --> 01:10:16,692
[growls]

987
01:10:18,360 --> 01:10:19,945
Tie his arms.

988
01:10:21,780 --> 01:10:23,782
[thunder rumbles]

989
01:10:29,413 --> 01:10:30,747
We have his name.

990
01:10:39,798 --> 01:10:41,258
"Bring me the priest."

991
01:10:42,593 --> 01:10:43,844
What did you say?

992
01:10:43,927 --> 01:10:47,806
Those were the first words the demon said.
"Bring me the priest."

993
01:10:49,224 --> 01:10:50,601
It didn't mean me.

994
01:10:51,185 --> 01:10:52,561
It wants you.

995
01:10:52,644 --> 01:10:55,022
This demon feeds on exorcists.

996
01:10:55,689 --> 01:10:57,357
He had a plan once.

997
01:10:58,650 --> 01:11:00,486
To lure the friar here,

998
01:11:01,320 --> 01:11:03,780
hide amongst the righteous
and commit heinous acts

999
01:11:03,864 --> 01:11:05,282
in the name of God.

1000
01:11:05,365 --> 01:11:07,576
He wants to do the same thing again.

1001
01:11:07,659 --> 01:11:10,412
Using me to infiltrate the Church.

1002
01:11:10,496 --> 01:11:12,706
What greater victory for the devil...

1003
01:11:14,500 --> 01:11:17,711
than to claim the soul
of the pope's exorcist?

1004
01:11:17,794 --> 01:11:20,589
Maybe. But we know his name now.

1005
01:11:21,798 --> 01:11:24,009
So we have what we need to beat it

1006
01:11:24,801 --> 01:11:26,470
and to save the child.

1007
01:11:27,429 --> 01:11:30,557
The only thing
that can defeat us is ourselves.

1008
01:11:33,602 --> 01:11:35,854
He will use your sins against you.

1009
01:11:39,816 --> 01:11:41,568
I need to make confession.

1010
01:11:42,236 --> 01:11:45,113
- To me?
- You are a priest, are you not?

1011
01:11:47,699 --> 01:11:50,118
Forgive me, Father, for I have sinned.

1012
01:11:51,203 --> 01:11:52,454
Trust in the Lord.

1013
01:11:55,832 --> 01:11:57,292
I want to talk to you...

1014
01:11:59,002 --> 01:12:01,421
about things I have confessed before...

1015
01:12:02,798 --> 01:12:04,424
but they still burden me.

1016
01:12:05,592 --> 01:12:07,219
In 1942...

1017
01:12:08,554 --> 01:12:10,639
during the war, I joined the Resistance.

1018
01:12:10,722 --> 01:12:13,350
I became a partisan
and I fought against the fascists.

1019
01:12:13,433 --> 01:12:15,936
[poignant music playing]

1020
01:12:16,019 --> 01:12:18,939
<i>So many of my friends
would die to German bullets.</i>

1021
01:12:21,858 --> 01:12:22,943
<i>Why them...</i>

1022
01:12:24,152 --> 01:12:25,571
and not me?

1023
01:12:27,281 --> 01:12:30,117
<i>Their dead bodies
would talk to me in my dreams.</i>

1024
01:12:31,493 --> 01:12:33,954
<i>To die in a war is heroic.</i>

1025
01:12:34,788 --> 01:12:36,206
To survive a war...

1026
01:12:37,624 --> 01:12:38,667
complex.

1027
01:12:42,713 --> 01:12:43,922
<i>And then I begin to see...</i>

1028
01:12:44,798 --> 01:12:46,550
<i>that my life had been spared.</i>

1029
01:12:46,633 --> 01:12:49,219
<i>It was my responsibility
to give it purpose.</i>

1030
01:12:49,303 --> 01:12:52,014
<i>And in my case, that meant to serve God.</i>

1031
01:12:54,850 --> 01:12:59,146
In all of my years, I have tried
to embrace what is said in Matthew.

1032
01:12:59,813 --> 01:13:04,526
<i>"What you do for the least among you,
you do for me."</i>

1033
01:13:05,527 --> 01:13:07,237
But when it mattered...

